## Examples  

 <span data-ttu-id="eca5a-102">El siguiente ejemplo se utiliza un <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Point3DConverter> estructura para convertir una cadena en un <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Point3D> estructura.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="eca5a-102">The following sample uses a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Point3DConverter> structure to convert a string into a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Media3D.Point3D> structure.</span></span>  

```csharp  
...  

// Converts a String to a Point3D using a Point3DConverter  
// Returns a Point3D.  

Point3DConverter p3DConverter = new Point3DConverter();  
Point3D point3DResult = new Point3D();  
string string3 = "10,20,30";  

point3DResult = (Point3D)p3DConverter.ConvertFromString(string3);  
// point3DResult is equal to (10, 20, 30)  

...  
```
